cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MS, cs.MM

The paper discusses the use of machine learning algorithms to accurately quantify emphysema extent from CT scans. This involves image analysis and classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also explores the use of different types of labels for training the algorithms, which is a topic related to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The evaluation of the algorithms involves statistical analysis (cs.MS) and comparison of results with human raters (cs.MM).
